name: Corneo's Marin Kitagawa TI Embedding
description:
This is a Textual Inversion Embedding of Marin Kitagawa from My Dress-Up Darling (sono bisque doll wa koi wo suru).

I wasn't familiar with the character when she came in as a request, so I watched My Dress-Up Darling over the weekend, was immediately hooked, binged the whole thing, and now I'm pretty obsessed and can't wait for season 2! So I really wanted to get this right and tinkered with it way too much.

It's mostly trained on both her school uniform and iconic bikini, so you can add tags to steer output towards either, though if you don't do that you'll sometimes get a mix of the two. My initial attempts had the multiple ear piercings as a focus but this really upset SD generating her ear properly, so you'll have to add prompts for earrings/piercings to get these consistently now. Same goes for the fake/long nails if you want those.

Example images created using my 7th Heaven mix https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
